  一类不连续广义Lienard微分系统的极限环
  Limit Cycles for a Class of Discontinuous Generalized Lienard Differential Systems
 
</article-title></title-group><contrib-group><contrib contrib-type="author" xlink:type="simple"><name name-style="western"><surname>余</surname><given-names>翠连</given-names></name><xref ref-type="aff" rid="aff1"><sub>1</sub></xref><xref ref-type="corresp" rid="cor1"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib></contrib-group><aff id="aff1"><label>1</label><addr-line>浙江师范大学，数理与信息工程学院，浙江 金华</addr-line></aff><author-notes><corresp id="cor1">* E-mail:<email>15268635636@163.com</email></corresp></author-notes><pub-date pub-type="epub"><day>16</day><month>01</month><year>2017</year></pub-date><volume>06</volume><issue>01</issue><fpage>20</fpage><lpage>28</lpage><permissions><copyright-statement>&#169; Copyright  2014 by authors and Scientific Research Publishing Inc. </copyright-statement><copyright-year>2014</copyright-year><license><license-p>This work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution International License (CC BY). http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/</license-p></license></permissions><abstract><p>
 
 
  利用Melnikov函数方法，我们研究从一类不连续广义Lienard微分系统的非线性中心的周期环域分支出极限环的最大个数问题。通过对该系统的非线性中心进行分段光滑的多项式扰动，得到了该系统从非线性中心的周期环域分支出极限环最大个数的估计。
   By using the Melnikov function theory, we study the maximum number of limit cycles which bi-furcate from the periodic annulus of the nonlinear center for a class of generalized Lienard diffe-rential systems. By piecewise smooth polynomial perturbating, the estimation of the maximum number of limit cycles which bifurcate from the periodic annulus of this nonlinear center is ob-tained.
 
</p></abstract><kwd-group><kwd>极限环，Melnikov函数，不连续系统，非线性中心, Limit Cycles</kwd><kwd> Melnikov Functions</kwd><kwd> Piecewise Systems</kwd><kwd> Nonlinear Center</kwd></kwd-group></article-meta></front><body><sec id="s1"><title>一类不连续广义Lienard微分系统的极限环<sup> </sup></title><p>余翠连</p><p>浙江师范大学，数理与信息工程学院，浙江 金华</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula145"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x6_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>收稿日期：2016年12月21日；录用日期：2017年1月9日；发布日期：2017年1月16日</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula146"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x7_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s2"><title>摘 要</title><p>利用Melnikov函数方法，我们研究从一类不连续广义Lienard微分系统的非线性中心的周期环域分支出极限环的最大个数问题。通过对该系统的非线性中心进行分段光滑的多项式扰动，得到了该系统从非线性中心的周期环域分支出极限环最大个数的估计。</p><p>关键词 :极限环，Melnikov函数，不连续系统，非线性中心</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula147"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x8_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s3"><title>1. 引言</title><p>众所周知，希尔伯特第16问题就是考虑平面多项式微分系统的极限环个数问题。但是对于一般的多项式微分系统，研究该问题是非常困难的，所以人们考虑了一些特殊的系统。比如Lienard微分系统</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula148"><label>(1)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x9_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>系统(1)的极限环个数问题一直被不断地研究，并且得到了许多经典的结果，如文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref1">1</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref2">2</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref3">3</xref>] 。</p><p>在文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref4">4</xref>] 中，作者把Lienard微分系统进行进一步推广，研究了下面广义Lienard微分系统</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula149"><label>(2)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x10_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x11_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x12_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是正整数，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x13_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是m次多项式，文章证明了从该系统非线性中心的周期环域最多分支出<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x14_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>个极限环。</p><p>然而，随着现实生活中出现许多不连续现象，越来越多的数学工作者开始研究不连续Lienard微分系统的分支问题。 例如文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref5">5</xref>] 考虑了下面不连续Lienard微分系统</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula150"><label>(3)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x15_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x16_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x17_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。运用不连续微分系统的一阶平均法，得到了该系统(3)</p><p>从中心的周期环域分支出极限环最大个数的线性估计。关于不连续微分系统更多的研究可见文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref6">6</xref>] [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref7">7</xref>] 。</p><p>鉴于不连续微分系统的重要性，本文讨论如下类型的不连续广义Lienard微分系统</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula151"><label>(4)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x18_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x19_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x20_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x21_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> (5)</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x22_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为正整数且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x23_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。</p><p>利用文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref8">8</xref>] 中介绍的Melnikov函数方法，本文考虑了系统(4)从非线性中心的周期环域分支出极限环的最大个数问题。我们的主要结果如下：</p><p>定理1.1 假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x24_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x25_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为系统(4)从非线性中心<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x26_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x27_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的周期环域分</p><p>支出来的极限环的最大个数。</p><p>(i) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x28_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x29_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>(ii) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x30_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x31_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>(iii) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x32_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x33_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>注：当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x34_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x35_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>、<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x36_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref9">9</xref>] 同样运用Melnikov函数证明了该不连续微分系统从线性中心</p><p>的周期环域可以分支出<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x37_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>个极限环。显然，文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref9">9</xref>] 的结果是定理1.1的结论(iii)的一种情</p><p>形。结果表明：在非线性中心的扰动下产生的极限环个数总是大于等于在线性中心扰动下的极限环个数，且极限环的个数与y的系数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x38_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是无关的。</p></sec><sec id="s4"><title>2. 预备知识</title><p>在这一部分，我们将介绍定理1.1证明过程所运用的Melnikov函数。考虑平面分段近Hamilton系统</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula152"><label>(6)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x39_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x40_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x41_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>可以表示成下面的形式</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula153"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x42_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>对系统(6)作以下假设：</p><p>(H1) 存在区间<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x43_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，系统(6)<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x44_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有一族顺时针周期轨道</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula154"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x45_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>(H2) 各周期轨道交轴于不同的两点<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x46_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x47_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x48_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，且<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x49_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x50_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>在假设(H1)和(H2)下，那么，由文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref8">8</xref>] 中的定理1.1 和文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref10">10</xref>] 中的引理2.2，可以得到系统(6)的Melnikov函数为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula155"><label>(7)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x51_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>这里<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x52_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x53_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>表示<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x54_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x55_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>.此时，确定系统(6)的极限环个数问题就转化为求一阶Melnikov函数孤立零点个数(重根按重数计算)的问题。由文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref11">11</xref>] 等式(7)等价于</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula156"><label>(8)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x56_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula157"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x57_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula158"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x58_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>此时，对于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x59_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x60_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>满足</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula159"><label>(9)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x61_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>从文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref11">11</xref>] 可知，若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在区间<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>有k个零点，则系统(6)从周期环域分支出k个极限环。所以只要考虑在(8)中第一个非零<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的零点个数就能够得到<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x65_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的零点个数。</p><p>在证明定理1.1之前，先给出一个在文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref12">12</xref>] 的引理：</p><p>引理1.1如果函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x66_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在实数R上是线性无关的，那么存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x67_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>,有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula160"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x69_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula></sec><sec id="s5"><title>3. 定理1.1的证明</title><p>为了运用函数(8)，我们令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x70_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>。为了方便运算，再把<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>用x，y表示，则系统(4)等价于</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula161"><label>(10)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x72_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>根据(8)式，系统(10)的一阶Melnikov函数为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula162"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x73_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula163"><label>(11)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x74_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>这里</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula164"><label>(12)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x75_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>易知系统(10)是分段近Hamilton系统，且它的Hamilton函数为</p><p><inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x76_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，</p><p>并且当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x77_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>时，系统(10)有一族周期轨道<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x78_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>在证明定理1.1过程中，我们得到以下引理：</p><p>引理3.1 如果函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x79_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x80_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>至多存在<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x81_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>个孤立的正零点。对于一些多项式<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x82_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x83_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，这零点的最大个数是可以取得的。且当多项式<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x84_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x85_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是奇函数时，函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x86_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>恒等于零。</p><p>证明：根据(5)，(10)，（12)和格林公式，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula165"><label>(13)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x87_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>通过运用格林公式和一般的Liapunov极坐标变换<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x88_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>(三角函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x89_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的详细介绍可见文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref13">13</xref>] )，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x90_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>可变为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula166"><label>(14)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x91_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>从文献 [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.19532-ref13">13</xref>] 可知</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula167"><label>(15)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x92_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>又根据(13)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula168"><label>(16)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x93_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>令<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x94_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，把(15)代入(14)，再把(14)，(16)代入(13)，有</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula169"><label>(17)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x95_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>在系统(4)中，可知p，q满足<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x96_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则(17)等价于</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula170"><label>(18)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x97_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula171"><label>(19)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x98_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>特别地，对于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x99_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，从上面分析可知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x100_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>. 根据(18)式，我们可以知道函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x101_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>至多有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x102_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>个孤立的正零点。显然<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x103_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是独立的，所以函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x104_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>孤立零点的最大个数是可以</p><p>得到的。同时根据(18)，(19)式也可以得到引理3.2。</p><p>引理3.2 假设<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x105_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是阶数分别为m,n的奇函数，那么函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x106_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>至多存在孤立的正零点个数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x107_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>为</p><p>(i) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x108_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x109_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>(ii) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x110_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x111_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>；</p><p>(iii) 若<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x112_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x113_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula></p><p>证明：其中沿着周期轨道<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x114_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，我们有<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x115_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则由(12)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula172"><label>(20)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x116_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>因为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x117_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是奇函数，则可得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula173"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x118_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>根据等式(12)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula174"><label>(21)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x119_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>由上述预备知识可知<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x120_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>和<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x121_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是满足下列方程的两个解</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula175"><label>(22)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x122_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>方程(22)两边对<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x123_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>求导得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula176"><label>(23)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x124_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>则</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula177"><label>(24)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x125_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>根据(11)，(18)得</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula178"><label>(25)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x126_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>因为<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x127_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是奇函数，所以<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x128_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>可以表示成</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula179"><label>(26)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x129_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>根据前面<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x130_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，则从(5)，(9)，(13)，(25)和(26)式可知</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula180"><label>(27)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x131_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula181"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x132_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>综合上述(11)，(18)，(20)，(27)式，则函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x133_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的表达式为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula182"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x134_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula183"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x135_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>函数<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x136_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的零点等价于<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x137_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>的零点，且</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.19532-formula184"><label>(28)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/3-2620358x138_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>为了计算